<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thirst-n">thirst <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /θɜːst/    美 /θɜːrst/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>渴；口渴：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>satisfy one’s thirst
解渴</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>渴望；热望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My <strong>thirst for knowledge</strong> was greater than my pains of hunger.
我对知识的渴望胜过饥饿的煎熬。</p></div></div>